  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://blazesportsintel.com
  Vary: Accept-Encoding
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin

# HTML Files - Short-term Caching with ETag
